column1: Great catching up with @ericbolling and @BlazeTV at #FFBBQ! 🇺🇸 https://t.co/etYd3Rzj70
Let’s take this momentum into 2020 to #KeepAmericaGreat! God bless the USA! (4/4) #FFBBQ

My friend Rep. @Jim_Jordan knocked it out of the park followed by an amazing keynote speech by our incredible @VP @Mike_Pence! This was all possible because of supporters like you — THANK YOU! (3/4) #FFBBQ

Rachel Lewis leading us in the Pledge the federal delegation of Senator @LindseyGrahamSC @RepTomRice @RalphNorman & @VoteTimmons Gov. @henrymcmaster & Lt. Gov. @PamelaEvette & the incredible @SteveAmerson — America’s Tenor. (2/4) #FFBBQ

Still reflecting on the #FFBBQ & how much patriotism & excitement was in the room! So many folks went into making the night a success — countless volunteers & supporters Creekside BBQ @SCGOP Chair @DrewMcKissick getting the crowd hyped up. (1/4)
Thank you @POTUS @realDonaldTrump!!! Keep America Great 🇺🇸 https://t.co/EZU6Ys1jzd
A special thanks to those we honored at the event - our veterans & first responders - who I’m immensely thankful for! It’s an honor to serve the people of #SC03! Thank you & God bless! #FFBBQ
Thank you to every single person for making #FFBBQ possible & for everyone’s support from near & far.
I’m humbled & filled with gratitude for the amount of support shown at the 2019 #FFBBQ & for a chance for all of us to come together to celebrate the #USA! https://t.co/M87826yMcq
